We should get into it.
I talked to my brother today.

45
00:03:03,583 --> 00:03:06,143
He knows of two other cases like that
at his firm.

46
00:03:06,252 --> 00:03:08,307
Let Platts know
that we're talking about it.

47
00:03:08,333 --> 00:03:09,574
Look, forget Platts.

48
00:03:09,656 --> 00:03:13,148
This has got to be about what
has the best chance of going to market...

49
00:03:13,159 --> 00:03:15,389
and what is going to get us VC attention.

50
00:03:15,495 --> 00:03:18,862
Look, I stuck by you guys
when it was your turn.

51
00:03:18,965 --> 00:03:21,763
And I wasn't 100% sure
of what we were doing...

52
00:03:21,868 --> 00:03:24,166
or even if I didn't agree, maybe.

53
00:03:25,405 --> 00:03:27,532
But if it's my turn...

54
00:03:27,774 --> 00:03:31,505
if we're still playing by the rules,
then this is what I want to try.

55
00:03:34,714 --> 00:03:37,046
Here, take it.
They said it wouldn't hold a freeze.

56
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:39,277
Robert, please. It's not going to hold.

57
00:03:39,385 --> 00:03:42,650
