- No, I didn't feel anything.

153
00:09:47,453 --> 00:09:49,751
That sound is just weirding me out.

154
00:09:55,428 --> 00:09:57,453
- What does it feel like?
- I don't know.

155
00:09:57,563 --> 00:09:59,724
I don't know if I'm making it up.

156
00:10:00,933 --> 00:10:02,195
Here.

157
00:10:16,549 --> 00:10:19,347
- Next part. Let's do the next part.
- Yeah.

158
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:30,693
Isn't there some sort of glass
or a transparent...

159
00:10:30,796 --> 00:10:33,356
