160
00:10:33,466 --> 00:10:35,093
- Yeah, I'm in.
- Okay, drop it.

161
00:10:35,201 --> 00:10:38,261
I don't know of anything
that won't leave a gap in the field.

162
00:10:38,371 --> 00:10:40,362
But we got to see what's going on in there.

163
00:10:40,473 --> 00:10:43,135
- How much did that cost?
- Yeah.

164
00:10:44,076 --> 00:10:46,772
- What?
- You want to put my camcorder...

165
00:10:46,879 --> 00:10:50,406
