we can't look into it.

166
00:10:53,886 --> 00:10:56,719
If something happens,
would you pay me back?

167
00:10:58,124 --> 00:11:01,616
So we have a slightly negative pressure
in the box.

168
00:11:01,894 --> 00:11:03,759
So we're ready for the argon.

169
00:11:04,497 --> 00:11:08,058
- Which one is that?
